ActAn Act to amend the Indian Act in response to the Superior Court of Quebec decision in Descheneaux c. Canada (Procureur général)
SubjectOrder Fixing August 15, 2019 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing August 15, 2019 as the day on which sections 2.1, 3.1, 3.2 and 10.1 of AN ACT TO AMEND THE INDIAN ACT IN RESPONSE TO THE SUPERIOR COURT OF QUEBEC DECISION IN DESCHENEAUX C. CANADA (PROCUREUR GÉNÉRAL), chapter 25 of the Statutes of Canada, 2017, COME INTO FORCE.
